# cargo-deb requires a maintainer-scripts directory to exist for its
# systemd-units integration to GENERATE the postinst/postrm enable/start/
# restart/stop scriptlets (dh_installsystemd style). This directory is
# intentionally otherwise empty: cargo-deb writes the scripts from scratch.
# (.gitkeep tracks the dir; cargo-deb ignores all but the known script names.)
